<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ar" dir="rtl">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>تواصل معنا</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/jqvmap/dist/jqvmap.min.css">
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/jquery@3.6.0/dist/jquery.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/jqvmap/dist/jquery.vmap.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/jqvmap/dist/maps/jquery.vmap.world.js"></script>
    <style>
        #vmap {
            width: 100%;
            height: 400px;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            #vmap {
                height: 300px;
            }
        }

        /* Améliorations pour les petits écrans */
        @media (max-width: 640px) {
            header h1 {
                font-size: 2.5rem;
            }

            header p {
                font-size: 1rem;
            }

            .container {
                padding-left: 1rem;
                padding-right: 1rem;
            }

            .bg-white {
                padding: 1.5rem;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body class="bg-gray-50">
{{> loginPrompt}}
    {{> header}}

    <!-- En-tête -->
    <header class=" text-black py-8 md:py-16 text-center px-4">
        <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-3">تواصل معنا</h1>
        <p class="text-base md:text-lg">إذا كان لديك أي استفسار، لا تتردد في التواصل معنا</p>
    </header>

    <!-- Contenu principal -->
    <main class="container mx-auto px-4 md:px-6 py-8 md:py-12">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 md:gap-12 items-center">

            <!-- Formulaire de contact -->
            <div class="bg-white p-6 md:p-8 rounded-lg shadow-lg order-2 md:order-1 transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-xl">
                <h2 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold mb-6 text-gray-800 border-b pb-3">أرسل لنا رسالة</h2>
                <form id="contactForm" action="/contact-us" method="POST" class="mt-4 md:mt-6 space-y-5">
                    <div class="mb-4 relative">
                        <label class="block text-gray-600 font-medium mb-2">الاسم الكامل</label>
                        <input type="text" id="name" name="name" autocomplete="off"
                            class="w-full px-4 py-3 border border-gray-300 rounded-lg focus:ring-2 focus:ring-green-500 focus:border-green-500 transition-all duration-200" required>
                    </div>
                    <div class="mb-4 relative">
                        <label class="block text-gray-600 font-medium mb-2">البريد الإلكتروني</label>
                        <input type="email" id="email" name="email" autocomplete="off"
                            class="w-full px-4 py-3 border border-gray-300 rounded-lg focus:ring-2 focus:ring-green-500 focus:border-green-500 transition-all duration-200" required>
                    </div>
                    <div class="mb-4 relative">
                        <label class="block text-gray-600 font-medium mb-2">رقم الجوال</label>
                        <input type="tel" id="phone" name="phone" autocomplete="off"
                            class="w-full px-4 py-3 border border-gray-300 rounded-lg focus:ring-2 focus:ring-green-500 focus:border-green-500 transition-all duration-200">
                    </div>
                    <div class="mb-6 relative">
                        <label class="block text-gray-600 font-medium mb-2">الرسالة</label>
                        <textarea id="message" name="message" rows="4" autocomplete="off"
                            class="w-full px-4 py-3 border border-gray-300 rounded-lg focus:ring-2 focus:ring-green-500 focus:border-green-500 transition-all duration-200"
                            required></textarea>
                    </div>
                    <button type="submit"
                        class="w-full bg-green-600 text-white py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-green-700 transition-all duration-300 transform hover:-translate-y-1 flex items-center justify-center">
                        <span>إرسال</span>
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 mr-2" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
                            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10.293 5.293a1 1 0 011.414 0l4 4a1 1 0 010 1.414l-4 4a1 1 0 01-1.414-1.414L12.586 11H5a1 1 0 110-2h7.586l-2.293-2.293a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                        </svg>
                    </button>
                </form>
                <div class="mt-6">
                    <p id="successMessage" class="text-green-600 text-center mt-4 hidden bg-green-50 p-3 rounded-lg border border-green-200">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 inline-block mr-1" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
                            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                        </svg>
                        تم إرسال رسالتك بنجاح!
                    </p>
                    <p id="errorMessage" class="text-red-600 text-center mt-4 hidden bg-red-50 p-3 rounded-lg border border-red-200">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 inline-block mr-1" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
                            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M18 10a8 8 0 11-16 0 8 8 0 0116 0zm-7 4a1 1 0 11-2 0 1 1 0 012 0zm-1-9a1 1 0 00-1 1v4a1 1 0 102 0V6a1 1 0 00-1-1z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                        </svg>
                        حدث خطأ أثناء إرسال الرسالة. حاول مرة أخرى.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Informations de contact -->
            <div class="order-1 md:order-2">
                <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold mb-6 text-gray-800">
                    خلال 6 سنوات، اشتغلت TN <span class="text-yellow-500">M3allim</span> في العديد من الدول حول العالم،
                    وتقدم خدماتها لعملائها في العديد من القارات.
                </p>

                <div class="row-scroll-cut">
                    <div id="vmap"></div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>

    {{> footer}}

